Gentle and iridescent Still is embodies the essential femininity of a soul at peace. Having traversed the long and winding road of life she has learned much and achieved inner peace. Sensual and alluring she is still true to herself. Created by perfumer Michel Girard for Jennifer Lopez Still is an Eau de Perfume that enshrouds you in a sheer mist of sensual serenity.

Clean and fresh Still opens with a shimmering top note of white pepper mandarin and Earl Grey tea infused with a hint of sake. An enchanting heart note of honeysuckle orange flower pink freesia jasmine lily of the valley and rose trails into a warm sensuous base note of sandal wood amber musk pepper and an earthy accord of orris. Vibrant yet tranquil Still is encased in a vial designed to look like a precious gem and adorned with a stunning solitaire.

Jennifer Lopez Glow Eau de Toilette - 100 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.2508

Every woman revels in the delicate moist steam that envelopes her after stepping out of an indulgent bath. As the gentle droplets trickle down her skin she is reminded of the misty allure that is Jennifer Lopez Glow. Spearheading the superstars foray into fragrances Glow is a luxury scent that celebrates the natural beauty of every woman. Created by Louise Turner in 2002 this Eau de Toilette embalms you in a breathtaking fog.

The top note opens with a delightful mix of sweet pink grapefruit slightly bitter hints of neroli and fragrant orange flower. Trailing after this is the heart of the fragrance drenched in the heady scent of tuberose clean and sweet iris along with aromatic jasmine citrus hints of orange blossom and the intense scent of fresh rose. Finally the base note strikes a chord with a deep-rooted scent profile comprising of exotic sandalwood creamy vanilla smoky amber and powerful hints of musk. The lovely combination of floral and woody accords refresh your senses with a clean and powdery scent that melts into your persona. This enchanting fragrance floats in a tall and scintillating frosted glass bottle with a slim neck that glides into a voluptuous base. The tender pink shade of the perfume that glows through the beautifully shaped foggy-glass bottle channels the beauty of the sensual female form. Adorned with a silver chain and rhinestone encrusted pendant Glow adds a new dimension to your daily beauty ritual. With a spritz of Jennifer Lopez Glow feel fresh out of the shower at any time of the day.
